OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTruss backtracks on public 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fworker pay plan            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Liz Truss has scrapped a plan to link  
OL,6, public sector pay to local living costs
OL,7, following a backlash from Tory MPs and 
OL,8, opposition parties.                    
OL,10,FThe Tory leadership candidate had      
OL,11,Fproposed regional pay boards, in a bid 
OL,12,Fto save taxpayers a potential #8.8bn.  
OL,14,FBut the policy was criticised by       
OL,15,Fseveral senior Tories, who argued it   
OL,16,Fwould mean lower pay for millions of   
OL,17,Fworkers outside London.                
OL,19,FMs Truss has now said the proposal     
OL,20,Fwould not be taken forward.            
